    "Primary antibodies were diluted in TBS with 1% BSA and 0.1% Tween20.",
    "Further, the staining was performed without blocking for peroxidases.",
    "For visualization the secondary antibodies ALEXA Fluor 647 donkey anti rabbit and ALEXA Fluor 488 donkey anti mouse (both Abcam, United Kingdom, Cambridge) were used and diluted as described above.",
    "Cell nuclei were stained with Hoechst.",
    "Finally, the slides were embedded in Mowiol-488 (Carl Roth, Karlsruhe, Germany)."
